1 Setup

1.1 Environment

Set the working dir

setwd("/mnt/picea/storage/reference/Populus-tremula/v1.1/")

Load the libraries

suppressPackageStartupMessages(library(Biostrings))
suppressPackageStartupMessages(library(genomeIntervals))
suppressPackageStartupMessages(library(RColorBrewer))
suppressPackageStartupMessages(library(VennDiagram))

Source some more file

source("~/Git/UPSCb/src/R/sequenceUtilities.R")
source("~/Git/UPSCb/src/R/gff3Utilities.R")

palette

pal <- brewer.pal(8,"Dark2")

Read in the input

gff3 <- readGff3(file = "gff3/Potra01-gene.gff3.gz",quiet=TRUE)
rep.gff3 <- readGff3(file = "gff3/Potra01-gene-representative.gff3.gz",quiet=TRUE)
genome <- readDNAStringSet("fasta/Potra01-genome.fa.gz")

existing output

old.cds <- readDNAStringSet("fasta/Potra01-CDS.fa.gz")
old.mRNA <- readDNAStringSet("fasta/Potra01-mRNA.fa.gz")
old.prot <- readAAStringSet("fasta/Potra01-protein.fa.gz")

r.old.cds <- readDNAStringSet("fasta/Potra01-representative-CDS.fa.gz")
r.old.mRNA <- readDNAStringSet("fasta/Potra01-representative-mRNA.fa.gz")
r.old.prot <- readAAStringSet("fasta/Potra01-representative-protein.fa.gz")

2 Extract anew

2.1 CDS

cds <- extractCdsFromGenome(gff3,genome)

2.2 mRNA

mRNA <- extractMrnaFromGenome(gff3,genome)

2.3 Protein

prot <- extractProteinFromGenome(gff3,genome)

                       filename=NULL,fill=pal[1:2]))

                       filename=NULL,fill=pal[1:2]))

4 Export

dir.create("fasta/inconsistent")
system("mv fasta/Potra01-CDS.fa.gz fasta/Potra01-mRNA.fa.gz fasta/Potra01-protein.fa.gz fasta/Potra01-representative-CDS.fa.gz fasta/Potra01-representative-mRNA.fa.gz fasta/Potra01-representative-protein.fa.gz fasta/inconsistent")
write("Moved the files in June 2017 as they are inconsistent with the v1.1 gff3. The fasta were re-extracted from the gff3 file.",file = "fasta/inconsistent/README")

writeXStringSet(cds,file="fasta/Potra01-CDS.fa.gz")
writeXStringSet(mRNA,file="fasta/Potra01-mRNA.fa.gz")
writeXStringSet(prot,file="fasta/Potra01-protein.fa.gz")
writeXStringSet(r.cds,file="fasta/Potra01-representative-CDS.fa.gz")
writeXStringSet(r.mRNA,file="fasta/Potra01-representative-mRNA.fa.gz")
writeXStringSet(r.prot,file="fasta/Potra01-representative-protein.fa.gz")
